item.title: MSc Thesis: Machine Learning for Analysis of Sarcoma
item.description: Description Early diagnosis of musculoskeletal tumours is crucial for successful therapy and treatment. The sooner a potential malignant growth is detected, the more effective the next steps in therapy and the better a prognosis usually becomes.
